# AsUpIO.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png)  ![:inline](/images/elmo.gif) 

### Description

AsUpIO.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: 8d97bb7f-e009-4dc7-ab9d-fde293e679dc
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Michael Haag, Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/magicsword-io/LOLDrivers/raw/main/drivers/9ba7c30177d2897bb3f7b3dc2f95ae0a.bin" "Download" >}}{{< button "https://www.magicsword.io/premium" "Block" "red" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create AsUpIO.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\AsUpIO.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start AsUpIO.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
